Comment: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chitose!
Comment: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning!
Comment: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?\NThe Johnny's idol group's Chinnen has a secret.
Comment: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Until just recently, he was a monk!
Comment: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way!
