Comment: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All girls at this age\Njust talk about romance and idols.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you into, Chitose?
Comment: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I definitely like Jun Maro!
Comment: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't get enough of that handsome face\Nthat doesn't look Japanese at all!
Comment: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Comment: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, doesn't Yamauchi\Nfrom Class 5 look a little bit like Jun Maro?
Comment: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, Yamauchi, with the soccer team?
Comment: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right! I like his eyebrows!
Comment: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is fun!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really do have to keep this a secret\Nfrom everyone at Yuragi Inn!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they saw me like this, I wouldn't be able\Nto maintain my authority as the manager.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chitose.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tsutomu!
Comment: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you having fun at school?
Comment: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see you\Nas a student at my school.
Comment: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I never imagined that brat with the missing\Nteeth would one day become a school principal.
Comment: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It makes you ponder.
Comment: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was decades ago.
Comment: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not many people have known\Nthat I'm a household protective deity,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the owner of Yuragi Inn and the Hot Springs\NAssociation have treated me very well.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's because of all of them\Nthat I can be here at this school.
Comment: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really are an eternal 13-year-old.
Comment: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, enjoy yourself.
Comment: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's been your dream to go to school, right?
Comment: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like a normal child.
Comment: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}YUKEMURI MART
Comment: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}MILK
Comment: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your waffle looks yummy, Chitose!
Comment: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it okay for middle school students\Nto spend money on sweets?
Comment: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure, why not? Don't be so stubborn.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A side trip with friends after school...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though it's at the shopping center\NI always go to, it's like a little adventure!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, girls!
Comment: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Want to go karaoke with us?
Comment: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-No thank you.
Comment: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ignore them and let's go.
Comment: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be like that!
Comment: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Comment: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're going to be a punk, then why don't you\Nstick to the part and act like real tough guys?
Comment: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean by punks?
Comment: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Comment: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aren't you embarrassed to dress up as lame\Njuvenile delinquents in this day and age?
Comment: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Our look is totally hot!
Comment: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My waffle!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luck manipulation...\NGood luck charm!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chitose, that was amazing!
Comment: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It was just a coincidence! A coincidence!
Comment: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, come on!
Comment: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you a ride on my motorcycle.
Comment: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't be shy.
Comment: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let go of me.
Comment: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't cut the crap,\NI'm going to get angry.
Comment: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, why am I letting a brat like this scare me?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-We're going!
Comment: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You give me no choice.
Comment: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Luck manipulation...
Comment: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Misfortune!
Comment: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is on you.\NI don't even know what's going to happen.
Comment: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All I know is you're about to be visited\Nby bad luck!
Comment: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let go of her.
Comment: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,These girls don't seem to like you guys.
Comment: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kogarashi?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
