Comment: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why you...
Comment: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Comment: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Comment: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Comment: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe Kogarashi happening\Nto be around would become their "bad luck."{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's also the bad luck reaction for me\Nafter the good luck I drew on before.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, thank you!
Comment: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please let me buy you some food as thanks!
Comment: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No need, no need!\NI'll be late for work, so see ya!
Comment: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wasn't he just so cool?
Comment: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder if he works near here.
Comment: 0,0:09:56.93,0:10:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems he didn't notice it was me.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...wherever and whenever,\NKogarashi is always Kogarashi.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, I should return to my usual self.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this world,\Nthere are various forms of good and bad luck.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Comment: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm home so late.
Comment: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's no better luck than meeting someone\Nwho makes you think, "I'm so glad we met."{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, which would you like first,\Na bath or dinner?
